document_data.Notable Owners:
[[Cogol]] and [[Harrik]], two [[ranger]] followers of [[Malar]] ''circa'' [[1372 DR]], tied tindertwigs to their smokesticks for ready ignition.<ref>{{Cite web/Fang, Beak, and Claw|4,5}}

Five tindertwigs were also part of the equipment of a [[Zhentarim]] acolyte of [[Bane]] that same year.<ref>

[[Gyudd]] of [[Gyudd's Distillery]] in [[Skullport]] kept ten of them as part of his equipment in 1375 DR.<ref>
